WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(c.color9CD5FF) { color: #9CD5FF; }
::cue(c.colora8c7fa) { color: #a8c7fa; }

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.000 line:0
<b><c.color9CD5FF>One Pace Premium</c></b>
Keep the project alive: <c.colora8c7fa>ko-fi.com/not6ip</c>

2
00:01:50.050 --> 00:01:54.890
For Whom the Bell Tolls

3
00:01:54.890 --> 00:01:56.850
H-He just...

4
00:01:56.850 --> 00:01:59.270
He broke Captain Kuro's cat claw!

5
00:02:02.350 --> 00:02:05.150
Only five of these
weird sword things left!

6
00:02:08.860 --> 00:02:11.070
It's okay! He has plenty
of fight left in him!

7
00:02:11.070 --> 00:02:13.070
Yeah! He's still got the other claw!

8
00:02:13.570 --> 00:02:16.700
Scratch him up
and kill him, Captain Kuro!

9
00:02:16.700 --> 00:02:19.830
Whoa, you can't call
him that anymore!

10
00:02:19.830 --> 00:02:23.540
Oh yeah... I think his name in
the village was Klaha... something...

11
00:02:23.540 --> 00:02:25.670
Mr. Klah, then!

12
00:02:25.670 --> 00:02:28.040
– Mr. Klah! Get 'im!
– Mr. Klah! Get 'im!

13
00:02:30.130 --> 00:02:31.960
Would you all just...

14
00:02:32.380 --> 00:02:33.380
shut the hell up?!

15
00:02:39.350 --> 00:02:41.720
Come on out, you twerps!

16
00:02:41.720 --> 00:02:44.350
I know you're hiding in there!

17
00:02:44.350 --> 00:02:45.940
Give it up already!

18
00:02:48.690 --> 00:02:50.150
Come over here!

19
00:02:50.150 --> 00:02:52.820
We'll take you straight to her!

20
00:02:55.030 --> 00:03:00.540
You really think I'm that gullible?
As if I'd trust anything you brats say!

21
00:03:01.540 --> 00:03:02.950
Huh?!

22
00:03:05.580 --> 00:03:07.040
We got him!

23
00:03:07.040 --> 00:03:08.040
Now!

24
00:03:10.550 --> 00:03:11.550
Take this!

25
00:03:11.550 --> 00:03:13.720
Pepper Attack!

26
00:03:29.980 --> 00:03:32.780
– Push!
– Push!

27
00:03:39.530 --> 00:03:41.280
Owww!

28
00:03:41.280 --> 00:03:42.910
Ow! Ow!

29
00:03:45.370 --> 00:03:48.420
– It's over, hypnotist!
– It's over, hypnotist!

30
00:03:53.710 --> 00:03:56.010
Don't get cocky.

31
00:03:57.340 --> 00:03:59.390
Darn it! We failed...!

32
00:03:59.930 --> 00:04:02.220
You've made a mockery of me.

33
00:04:02.220 --> 00:04:04.970
But I am still a pirate...

34
00:04:07.140 --> 00:04:08.270
– Onion!
– Onion!

35
00:04:08.270 --> 00:04:13.110
You wannabe pirate brats poked
your noses in a bit too deep...

36
00:04:16.900 --> 00:04:19.280
Where are you hiding, Miss?!

37
00:04:19.280 --> 00:04:22.780
I'll start by executing these three.

38
00:04:22.780 --> 00:04:26.870
You can reflect on your poor choice
to meddle with real pirates...

39
00:04:26.870 --> 00:04:30.370
on your way to the afterlife.

40
00:04:37.470 --> 00:04:39.340
There you are.

41
00:04:40.590 --> 00:04:41.890
No!

42
00:04:41.890 --> 00:04:43.300
Run, Miss Kaya!

43
00:04:43.300 --> 00:04:44.180
Hey!

44
00:04:44.180 --> 00:04:46.350
Yeah! That's them!

45
00:04:46.350 --> 00:04:47.770
It's the other way?!

46
00:04:49.060 --> 00:04:54.190
I'll eliminate each and every
one of you later...

47
00:04:54.860 --> 00:04:57.780
That includes Jango!

48
00:04:57.780 --> 00:05:00.610
Wh-Why us?!

49
00:05:00.610 --> 00:05:03.740
Please stop joking around,
Captain Kuro!

50
00:05:04.120 --> 00:05:07.500
It's still not too late for us
to attack the village, right?!

51
00:05:07.500 --> 00:05:12.710
And if Captain Jango gets her to write
her will, your plan will succeed!

52
00:05:13.840 --> 00:05:17.000
Do not concern yourselves
with the details of my plan...

53
00:05:17.000 --> 00:05:22.130
All I need from you are corpses
on which to pin the blame.

54
00:05:23.340 --> 00:05:27.770
I never intended to let any of
you leave this village alive.

55
00:05:28.390 --> 00:05:34.230
I can't let anyone who
knows my true identity live.

56
00:05:34.610 --> 00:05:35.570
No way...

57
00:05:35.570 --> 00:05:39.690
Then you planned to kill us
from the very start?!

58
00:05:41.400 --> 00:05:43.660
That's right...

59
00:05:44.030 --> 00:05:49.450
For three long years now, back when
I was still going by Captain Kuro...

60
00:05:49.450 --> 00:05:51.580
it was all...

61
00:05:52.080 --> 00:05:54.580
it was all part of my plan!

62
00:05:56.590 --> 00:05:58.800
Man, you guys are dumb.

63
00:05:58.800 --> 00:06:01.050
Your pirate crew is so lame!

64
00:06:02.130 --> 00:06:03.890
"Lame"?

65
00:06:03.890 --> 00:06:09.100
In the end, a pirate crew
is nothing but a pack of stray dogs!

66
00:06:09.430 --> 00:06:12.520
What could they possibly
accomplish without a plan?!

67
00:06:12.520 --> 00:06:16.770
Every last one should just
shut up and follow my orders!

68
00:06:17.570 --> 00:06:21.110
Crew members are
a captain's loyal pawns!

69
00:06:21.110 --> 00:06:25.030
I'm the one who decides
whether to kill them or spare them.

70
00:06:25.030 --> 00:06:29.830
No matter how great the obstacle,
they simply need to stand up to it...

71
00:06:29.830 --> 00:06:33.290
and die according to my plans.

72
00:06:34.870 --> 00:06:37.710
This is what it means to be a pirate!

73
00:06:37.710 --> 00:06:40.800
Don't patronize me, you little vagrant!

74
00:06:45.930 --> 00:06:47.890
Even if a captain like you...

75
00:06:48.260 --> 00:06:51.430
had hundreds or thousands
of men following him...

76
00:06:52.520 --> 00:06:55.230
you'd never be better than Usopp!

77
00:06:57.230 --> 00:06:59.110
What?!

78
00:06:59.730 --> 00:07:03.860
You're saying I'm inferior to a kid
pretending to be a pirate captain?

79
00:07:03.860 --> 00:07:04.700
That's right!

80
00:07:07.240 --> 00:07:09.120
How droll!

81
00:07:09.120 --> 00:07:13.200
Don't get cocky just because
you snapped one of my claws!

82
00:07:13.540 --> 00:07:15.670
How exactly is he better than me?!

83
00:07:16.170 --> 00:07:17.630
Let's hear it!

84
00:07:22.130 --> 00:07:23.590
Character.

85
00:07:24.470 --> 00:07:25.840
What?!

86
00:07:25.840 --> 00:07:31.720
You have no idea
what it means to be a pirate!

87
00:07:42.270 --> 00:07:43.990
H-He...

88
00:07:43.990 --> 00:07:47.450
He kept up with
the Pussyfoot Maneuver!

89
00:07:49.910 --> 00:07:52.790
How insulting...

90
00:07:54.830 --> 00:08:00.790
If you're curious about real pirates,
then allow me to demonstrate...

91
00:08:00.790 --> 00:08:03.380
true terror.

92
00:08:03.750 --> 00:08:09.550
The terror of a pirate who has
faced death countless times!

93
00:08:14.520 --> 00:08:17.230
Hey! That stance! Is he...?!

94
00:08:17.230 --> 00:08:19.230
That's the move he's gonna use?!

95
00:08:19.230 --> 00:08:21.650
But he's only fighting one guy!

96
00:08:21.650 --> 00:08:23.440
But that's definitely it!

97
00:08:23.440 --> 00:08:26.900
He's planning to use
Whole Nine Yarns!

98
00:08:28.280 --> 00:08:29.910
Aren't we in danger here?!

99
00:08:29.910 --> 00:08:31.280
He'll get us, too!

100
00:08:31.280 --> 00:08:33.030
He already plans to kill us!

101
00:08:33.030 --> 00:08:34.870
He even said so earlier!

102
00:08:35.450 --> 00:08:36.950
Please stop, Captain Kuro!

103
00:08:36.950 --> 00:08:38.500
Anything but that!

104
00:08:38.500 --> 00:08:40.250
We'll do anything you want!

105
00:08:40.250 --> 00:08:43.000
Please, Captain Kuro!

106
00:08:43.000 --> 00:08:44.340
What's the big deal?

107
00:08:45.090 --> 00:08:47.800
He's just swaying back and forth...

108
00:08:47.800 --> 00:08:50.470
– Please stop, Captain Kuro!
– Please stop, Captain Kuro!

109
00:08:50.970 --> 00:08:52.300
Whole Nine Yarns!

110
00:09:02.440 --> 00:09:04.020
What a pitiful haul...

111
00:09:04.650 --> 00:09:07.990
I thought they'd have a little
more treasure than that...

112
00:09:08.440 --> 00:09:11.530
Let's see, is the fight over yet?

113
00:09:13.160 --> 00:09:14.490
What?

114
00:09:14.490 --> 00:09:16.240
Nobody's moving...

115
00:09:16.240 --> 00:09:17.700
Is it over?

116
00:09:25.750 --> 00:09:26.590
There it is!

117
00:09:28.210 --> 00:09:30.760
Wh-Why's he over there?!

118
00:09:33.140 --> 00:09:34.470
Not again!

119
00:09:36.220 --> 00:09:37.600
Now it's the wall!

120
00:09:43.600 --> 00:09:46.070
Please stop, Captain Kuro!

121
00:09:46.070 --> 00:09:49.030
It's no use! His Pussyfoot Maneuver
attacks are out of control!

122
00:09:49.030 --> 00:09:52.860
He's moving so fast he doesn't
even know what he's slashing!

123
00:09:53.530 --> 00:09:56.080
He's already cut down
so many of our cr–

124
00:09:57.160 --> 00:09:58.080
Hey!

125
00:10:03.540 --> 00:10:06.040
Wh-What's happening?!

126
00:10:06.040 --> 00:10:08.550
They're getting all sliced up
out of nowhere!

127
00:10:23.060 --> 00:10:24.440
Show yourself...

128
00:10:25.020 --> 00:10:25.900
butler...

129
00:10:39.030 --> 00:10:43.790
Don't you care about
your crew at all?!

130
00:10:46.250 --> 00:10:47.540
Luffy...

131
00:11:13.320 --> 00:11:14.780
Found you!

132
00:11:15.400 --> 00:11:16.910
Sly bastard!

133
00:11:16.910 --> 00:11:19.740
You should've let me cut you down
like a good little boy!

134
00:11:19.740 --> 00:11:20.870
Look!

135
00:11:20.870 --> 00:11:26.420
My poor men are suffering dearly,
and it's all thanks to you!

136
00:11:26.420 --> 00:11:30.040
It would've been kinder if you'd
just let my attack kill them!

137
00:11:33.050 --> 00:11:35.130
Now what?

138
00:11:35.130 --> 00:11:37.220
You look like you have
something to say...

139
00:11:37.220 --> 00:11:38.010
Yeah...

140
00:11:38.430 --> 00:11:40.180
No matter what...

141
00:11:42.100 --> 00:11:44.140
I will never be like you.

142
00:11:44.140 --> 00:11:46.350
Never will...?

143
00:11:48.100 --> 00:11:51.980
More like never can.
Not someone like you, anyway.

144
00:11:54.400 --> 00:11:55.820
Though it doesn't matter...

145
00:11:56.530 --> 00:11:58.820
since you're going to die here anyway.

146
00:12:00.070 --> 00:12:02.330
Please stop this!

147
00:12:02.330 --> 00:12:04.160
Leave them alone!

148
00:12:04.950 --> 00:12:06.790
I'll write the will!

149
00:12:06.790 --> 00:12:08.170
N-No!

150
00:12:08.580 --> 00:12:12.000
They'll kill you if you
write it, Miss Kaya!

151
00:12:12.000 --> 00:12:15.840
You've got the wrong idea. There are
no negotiations to be had here.

152
00:12:15.840 --> 00:12:19.550
Captain Kuro told me
to get rid of everyone.

153
00:12:19.550 --> 00:12:20.800
You can't be serious!

154
00:12:28.640 --> 00:12:32.650
Do as I say, or I'll take my own life!

155
00:12:32.650 --> 00:12:33.980
That means no will!

156
00:12:33.980 --> 00:12:35.940
Wh-Wh-Whoa! Just hold on!

157
00:12:35.940 --> 00:12:36.990
Don't be hasty!

158
00:12:37.320 --> 00:12:40.860
I absolutely must get you
to write that will!

159
00:12:41.620 --> 00:12:43.240
M-Miss Kaya!

160
00:12:45.870 --> 00:12:48.040
Fine! The twerps can go!

161
00:12:48.540 --> 00:12:52.170
Though they're really
in no condition to run...

162
00:12:55.920 --> 00:12:57.460
Sign it, too!

163
00:12:57.460 --> 00:12:58.800
I know...

164
00:13:02.090 --> 00:13:05.890
"I leave my entire estate
to my butler, Klahadore..."

165
00:13:05.890 --> 00:13:06.970
Excellent!

166
00:13:06.970 --> 00:13:08.850
This is your will, all right!

167
00:13:08.850 --> 00:13:11.730
And I didn't even have
to hypnotize you!

168
00:13:12.860 --> 00:13:16.690
You promise not to kill them, right?

169
00:13:18.320 --> 00:13:19.820
Don't worry.

170
00:13:19.820 --> 00:13:23.280
I might not look like it,
but I'm a man of my word.

171
00:13:23.280 --> 00:13:25.330
– Miss Kaya!
– Miss Kaya!

172
00:13:26.540 --> 00:13:27.830
There they are!

173
00:13:27.830 --> 00:13:31.790
There they are! There they are! Stop!

174
00:13:27.830 --> 00:13:29.910
Owww! Ow, ow, ow!

175
00:13:29.910 --> 00:13:31.790
That's where I got cut, you know!

176
00:13:31.790 --> 00:13:33.080
Over there!

177
00:13:35.340 --> 00:13:36.420
Alright, I'll be back!

178
00:13:36.420 --> 00:13:37.340
Hey!

179
00:13:38.010 --> 00:13:40.510
That's far enough, hypno-freak!

180
00:13:41.590 --> 00:13:43.590
He came after me?!

181
00:13:49.560 --> 00:13:54.060
Guess I'd better finish this quickly!

182
00:13:58.650 --> 00:14:01.030
Everything before now
was just an appetizer.

183
00:14:02.780 --> 00:14:04.530
You get the three-course treatment.

184
00:14:06.080 --> 00:14:11.710
I will baste you in terror and
serve you meticulously on a platter!

185
00:14:14.290 --> 00:14:15.540
Whole Nine Yarns!

186
00:14:37.190 --> 00:14:38.980
Just try that foot technique now!

187
00:14:38.980 --> 00:14:41.240
Curses! Get off of me!

188
00:14:41.610 --> 00:14:45.910
Now your three-year plan
is a complete failure!

189
00:14:45.910 --> 00:14:47.410
What?!

190
00:14:47.410 --> 00:14:50.330
He caught Captain Kuro!

191
00:14:50.870 --> 00:14:55.870
Hey, if he wins, that means
we won't get killed, right?!

192
00:14:57.840 --> 00:15:00.170
Now you die!

193
00:15:00.170 --> 00:15:02.550
Oh, no, you don't!

194
00:15:07.930 --> 00:15:11.100
You damn kids!

195
00:15:13.770 --> 00:15:15.850
You're just one step
too late, bellyband!

196
00:15:15.850 --> 00:15:17.400
You sure about that?

197
00:15:21.110 --> 00:15:23.940
Yes! That branch was in the way!

198
00:15:25.200 --> 00:15:26.320
What?!

199
00:15:26.320 --> 00:15:27.490
Usopp...

200
00:15:28.240 --> 00:15:29.370
– Captain!
– Captain!

201
00:15:30.370 --> 00:15:32.620
Eat this, hypnotist!

202
00:15:32.620 --> 00:15:34.910
Get 'im, rubber guy!

203
00:15:34.910 --> 00:15:36.920
Kick Captain Kuro's ass!

204
00:15:37.460 --> 00:15:38.670
Get away!

205
00:15:39.840 --> 00:15:44.420
You guys don't get to cheer for me!

206
00:15:45.010 --> 00:15:46.800
Let go!

207
00:15:46.800 --> 00:15:49.510
Gum-Gum...

208
00:15:50.180 --> 00:15:52.350
Lethal Exploding Star!

209
00:15:55.560 --> 00:15:57.440
My plan...

210
00:15:56.390 --> 00:16:03.360
...Bell!

211
00:15:57.440 --> 00:16:03.360
My plan cannot fail!
